in tempaltetags/fsm-admin.py:
This will make it possible to use  custom=dict('verbose') in @transition

By example: 
58 line code
```
if 'verbose' in transition.custom::
    return '{0} {1}'.format(transition.custom['verbose'], model_name).title()
else:
